# Trigger Reference

Quick reference for all available triggers in the MyVoice context system.

## Setup & Git

| Trigger | Purpose | Output |
|---------|---------|--------|
| `/setup` | Initial setup wizard | Creates private/ files interactively |
| `/setup quick` | Quick setup | Creates template files to fill manually |
| `/push` | Safe git push | Validates architecture, scans for PII |
| `/push status` | Preview push | Shows what would be committed |
| `/gitignore check` | Verify .gitignore | Confirms private data is excluded |

## Session Management

| Trigger | Purpose | Output |
|---------|---------|--------|
| `/first` | Morning kickoff | Creates daily report, archives yesterday's |
| `/first quiet` | Silent morning kickoff | Creates report without prompts |
| `/close` | End-of-session refresh | Walks through context updates |
| `/weekly` | Weekly review | Progress, retro, planning |
| `/review` | Full context verification | Verifies all items, updates timestamps |
| `/review quick` | Quick verification | Abbreviated Y/N check |

